txt.en: Glowing ore can be found inside Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft.\n\nYou should mine the glowing ore for Atli Spider-bane.
Atli Spider-bane has requested an adventurer to mine a mysterious ore in Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft.

A note hangs on the board, signed by Atli Spider-bane:\n\n'I spotted a glowing ore I've never seen before in the Kâm Lagúrz, the Brokencleft. If any of you are brave enough to venture inside, bring me some samples!'
